	heroEyebrow={`A Father For`}
	heroSubhead={`Job loss, debt, rent that keeps climbing, the quiet shame of falling behind — financial hardship is one of the heaviest weights a person can carry. Here's the truth underneath the numbers: you have a Father in heaven who knows exactly what you need, provides for the birds of the air, and loves you no matter what your account says.`}
