	offersHeading={`What "our Father" offers you`}
	offersIntroHtml={`Financial hardship asks you to carry it alone and to measure yourself by what you have. Here's what your Father gives you instead — freely, because you're already His.`}
	offersBlocks={[
		{ heading: `A Father who knows your needs`, bodyHtml: `You don't have to inform God of the shortfall — <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/matthew/6" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father already knows what you need</a> before you ask, and He tells you not to be ruled by the worry.` },
		{ heading: `Provision for your real needs`, bodyHtml: `This isn't name-it-and-claim-it. It's the promise that <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/philippians/4" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your God will supply every need of yours</a> according to His riches — a supply that doesn't run dry when yours does.` },
		{ heading: `A Shepherd when you're in want`, bodyHtml: `"I shall not want" isn't denial of the hardship — it's trust in the One who leads you through it. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/23" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">The Lord is your shepherd</a>, and He makes sure you lack nothing you truly need.` },
		{ heading: `A presence nothing can repossess`, bodyHtml: `No creditor, no layoff, no empty account can touch this: <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/hebrews/13" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">"I will never leave you nor forsake you."</a> When everything else feels uncertain, your Father stays.` },
	]}
	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for financial hardship`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a providing Father, not a rulebook`, bodyHtml: `Most Bibles can read like a ledger of demands. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. So instead of one more voice telling you to do better with money, you meet the One who feeds the birds and knows your needs.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio`, bodyHtml: `When nothing is what you have, this costs nothing. No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen on the bus, on a job search, or when the worry hits at 2 a.m. The Father's voice fits into your real, stretched day.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to what you're actually facing`, bodyHtml: `Anxious about money? Carrying shame? Wondering if God even sees? Start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or learn to bring the need to Him with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you right where you are.` },
